{"tid":739066,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"17環保人士爬摩天輪示威罰款2千　離庭不忘呼籲關注污染問題","createTime":"2018-07-12T00:00:53.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-12T03:12:58.000Z","uid":81228,"like":2,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"e58a8eb87a507cf3b3d540c1e65692a069161c65","tid":739066,"uid":81228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-12T00:00:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/1634723/org/aea7b42630be7bd5702b3ddfe0986f5d.jpg/uRlcuJf53ertPxrhaoYTfy1rcwHyX8hhrRZGQq0WRkI?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1634723%2Forg%2Faea7b42630be7bd5702b3ddfe0986f5d.jpg%2FuRlcuJf53ertPxrhaoYTfy1rcwHyX8hhrRZGQq0WRkI%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=e04b2ff2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n19名環保組織綠色和平成員和義工，去年12月闖入中環摩天輪範圍示威，更有人爬上摩天輪企圖展示「夠鐘走塑」的橫額，被控「擅入機動遊戲機」罪。早前兩名外籍被告已被定罪，今（11日）其餘17名被告亦認罪，同被判罰款2千元。其中一名於綠色和平工作的被告，離庭不忘呼籲大眾正視塑膠污染帶來的社會問題。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/1634730/org/8edbe7e2bb6818fcc17fa8f99ee739bd.jpg/0QWLE6RpX295ciNqx5pzqUmoWaU-s47dW6YJv1umCb8?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1634730%2Forg%2F8edbe7e2bb6818fcc17fa8f99ee739bd.jpg%2F0QWLE6RpX295ciNqx5pzqUmoWaU-s47dW6YJv1umCb8%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=9f078700&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n綠色和平項目主任李逸燊（左二）離庭不忘呼籲大眾關注污染問題。（許家希攝）<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/1553312/org/f9fd9f008d697c814a565d332c62b032.jpg/0B19obJdwIMbamkn1B4gF2u5E4ivPodbr4Yuoa-GLqE?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1553312%2Forg%2Ff9fd9f008d697c814a565d332c62b032.jpg%2F0B19obJdwIMbamkn1B4gF2u5E4ivPodbr4Yuoa-GLqE%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=fbfba7cb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/1071181/org/2ed3aa12f9d0d93862ae1bccdae2a256.JPG/4WcyGKm2sv_UROEwiVxqooKFUxKCB5VU2Urxg9lK8YM?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmed